2.5.40.name: wordpress/blognetworking
2.5.40.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

BlogNetworking allows networks of blogs to share headlines through a central feed of associate sites. To avoid performance problems the feed will be cached locally

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find BlogNetworking useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain BlogNetworking

BlogNetworking is written by dcoda

You can check out our other plugins here
